			<description source="Gerhard Schoenhofer" lang="en" script="latn">On this advertisement for the Monotype Corporation Ltd., a sample of the advertised product can be seen as well as representatives of four different regional language groups in India plus some samples of their local scripts. The lower section hosts adress details from different branches of the advertising company.</description>
