"many languages in many founts"</text>
			</inscription>
			<inscription>
				<author/>
				<position/>
				<text type="text" lang="en">A "Monotype" machine sets and casts SINGLE type in hard metal. The independent keyboard accommodates a vast range of characters. The caster automatically casts and sets lines of perfectly-spaced type ready to print. No other composing machine has such a range of capability with maximum output.</text>
